sequenceDiagram
    actor Client
    participant API as FastAPI Router
    participant Game as GameService
    participant Calc as GuessCalculator
    participant Dmg as DamageCalculator
    participant Boss as BossAi
    participant Repo as GameRepository

    Client->>API: POST /games/{gameId}/guesses
    API->>Game: submitPlayerGuess
    Game->>Calc: score guess vs boss secret
    Game->>Dmg: apply damage to boss
    Game->>Repo: persist guess + boss hp
    alt boss hp zero
        Game->>Repo: outcome players_win
    else player queue exhausted
        Game->>Boss: run boss round
        Boss->>Calc: score vs player secrets
        Boss->>Dmg: damage or heal
        Game->>Repo: persist boss round hits
    end
    Game-->>API: GuessTurnResult
    API-->>Client: 200 GuessTurnResult
